      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental data reports flow rates of 2.5–6 L/min and rotational speeds of 2000–3500 RPM. Simulation boundary conditions replicate these within 2.3% maximum deviation. Fluid properties set to match blood analog (glycerin-water, 37°C)."
    },
